  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b90.\u0bae.\u0b9a. \u0b85\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Anti-government protest at Purakkottai railway station: UNP urges all to attend. Call",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The only thing left to them today is the sovereignty to remove the rulers who have put the people in dire straits.",
        "There is no other alternative. Therefore, the United People's Power has invited everyone to participate in the anti-government demonstration organized at the Colombo-Purrakottai Railway Station premises today, Thursday, the 30th at 3.30 p.m.",
        "This was stated by Member of Parliament Mujibur Rahman at a press conference held at the office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo on Wednesday (29).",
        "Sovereign power lies with the people who elected the rulers. If the rulers are elected by the people, then the people have the power to remove them from power. The world has a history of dictatorships and rulers being ousted by the people.",
        "We have tabled a motion of no confidence in Parliament to democratically remove these rulers.",
        "But none of them allowed Gotabhaya Rajapakse's colleagues to execute. That is why there is a need for the people to use the sovereign power of the people beyond the parliament.",
        "The only power left for the people of this country at present is to remove the rulers from office. We therefore call on the people to come forward and fight in the streets to remove these rulers from office.",
        "We call on all to unite to defeat the rulers who have put us and our future generations in crisis.",
        "We invite you to visit the Colombo - Purakkottai Railway Station premises on the 30th at 3.30 pm on the same day.",
        "We are calling on all the people of Colombo to use our sovereignty to surround the Presidential Palace where President Gotabaya Rajapaksa resides."
      ],
